    </h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Generate shell commands that work the first time‚Äîwithout sending your production data to the cloud.
      Caro runs 100% locally and blocks dangerous commands before you can execute them.
    </p>

    <div class="social-proof">
      <div class="quote">
        "I almost deleted our production database at 3 AM. Caro stopped me."
      </div>
      <div class="attribution">‚Äî Senior SRE at a Fortune 500</div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-section">
